::Feline::

She looked at Zardus. She smiled. But behind her smile, she had ideas 
running through her head.  This Zardus is one tough bot, she thought. 
She was stumped at to how to get him to even like her.  She still had 
plenty of trick in her bag, but she could usually tell which ones 
would work on a bot.  But Zardus had her stumped.  She would have to 
wait until the end of the mission to find out just what buttons to 
push on Zardus.  She didn't know for sure, but she was getting a few 
ideas.
